																		Author Post
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610205746" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;" >Grigori Karpin</a></span> <span class="odate time_1601347683 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">29 Sep 2020 02:48</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4784206">
									

<p>This is the hub for our contest entry series for CanCon2020 - <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Resurrection: New Faces</span></strong>.</p>
<p>I want to thank my teammates for their input <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604128906" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5379342); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5379342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604128906" alt="redredred" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5379342)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5379342); return false;">redredred</a></span> and especially <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604128906" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span> for making the base hub which I changed and included the top most image.</p>
<p>The image is intended to inspire curiosity as to the nature of our tales, but also, I think it looks cool (which i hope it does, as it took hours of work with my ignorant self messing with photo editing software).</p>
<p>Also thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604128906" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;">HarryBlank</a></span> for checking out everything I do, as always.</p>
<hr />
<p>To me, Resurrection has always been about looking forward to the future. Taking what used to be taboo (in this context the Foundation partnering up with anomalies) and normalizing it. I've always thought this canon had wide open opportunities for stories of a cinematic nature.</p>
<p>Which is why i wanted to tell a new story that fits into the world set out in the existing canon, which is luckily also what my teammates wanted to do. It's also why we've added a bunch of characters for this subset of Alpha-9.</p>
<hr />
<p>I hope you enjoy our story, and if you're curious about some of the other stuff I've done, please check out my author page:</p>
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/grigori-karpin-s-author-page">Grigori's Author Page</a></p>

							</div>

								
