			<div class="content" id="post-content-4820536">
									

<p>Adjacent. The idea that one centralized team was the biggest flaw in Omega-7 was put forth by Light in an early Rez tale (I believe when they first went to her to get her to Direct) and we followed that to a natural conclusion: Sophia Light was never going to stick with just the one squad on MYF-Alpha-9.</p>
<p>Moreover, as the original storyline isn’t finished, we didn’t want to step on any toes concerning the narrative. So we intentionally set this up as a separate but related story.</p>
<p>Additionally, as I definitely wanted to continue the story, we wanted to make an independent set of characters that could be utilized within the canon. In fact, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605588915" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;">HarryBlank</a></span> and I are collaborating on a sequel series starring some of his Rez team’s characters and some of ours!</p>
<p>So glad you enjoyed!</p>

							</div>

								
